<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="date=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="address=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="email=no">
    <title>Balance Payment Confirmation - {{quoteReference}}</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <noscript>
        <xml>
            <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
                <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
            </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Reset styles */
        body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        table, td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }
        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            border: 0;
            height: auto;
            line-height: 100%;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #9568b0;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #9568b0;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .main-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .payment-details {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .payment-row {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .payment-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666666;
        }
        
        .payment-value {
            color: #333333;
        }
        
        .amount {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #9568b0;
        }
        
        .complete-notice {
            background-color: #f0f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #b8e3e9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        
        .unsubscribe {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #999999;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100% !important;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px !important;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 20px 15px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Balance Payment Confirmed</h1>
            <p>Quote #{{quoteReference}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{customerName}},</div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                Your balance payment has been successfully processed. Your move is now fully paid and confirmed.
            </div>
            
            <div class="payment-details">
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Quote Reference:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">#{{quoteReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Balance Paid:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value amount">£{{balanceAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">£{{totalAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Payment Date:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">{{paymentDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="complete-notice">
                <h3>Payment Complete</h3>
                <p>Your move is now fully paid and confirmed. We look forward to providing you with professional service on your moving day.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Your payment is now complete and confirmed</li>
                    <li>Our team will contact you to finalize moving details</li>
                    <li>You'll receive updates about your booking via email</li>
                    <li>We'll be in touch closer to your moving date</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                <p><strong>Need help?</strong> If you have any questions about your payment or booking, please contact our support team at support@tranzrmoves.com or call us at 0800 123 4567.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <p><strong>Tranzr Moves</strong></p>
                <p>Professional Moving Services</p>
                <p>Email: support@tranzrmoves.com | Phone: 0800 123 4567</p>
                <p>© {{currentYear}} Tranzr Moves. All rights reserved.</p>
                
                <div class="unsubscribe">
                    <p>You received this email because you made a balance payment for quote #{{quoteReference}}. If you have any concerns about this email, please contact us at support@tranzrmoves.com.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>